WEBVTT

00:02.829 --> 00:04.879
Daniel, what are you doing?

00:05.315 --> 00:07.119
It is time to have breakfast.

00:08.281 --> 00:09.939
I'm washing my face.

00:10.533 --> 00:12.062
What time is it now, Mom?

00:13.191 --> 00:14.991
It is a half past seven.

00:15.371 --> 00:16.559
You need to hurry.

00:19.675 --> 00:22.365
Janice, are you ready to go to school?

00:23.384 --> 00:24.040
Not yet.

00:24.478 --> 00:26.117
I'm putting on my jacket.

00:27.193 --> 00:28.373
Hurry up, Janice.

00:28.763 --> 00:30.389
It's already 8 o'clock.

00:31.461 --> 00:32.450
Okay, Mom.

00:39.444 --> 00:42.582
It is time for Ben to go to bed.

00:43.200 --> 00:45.427
Ben gets ready for bed.

00:46.941 --> 00:48.659
He takes off his clothes.

00:48.812 --> 00:49.536
Plop, plop.

00:50.475 --> 00:52.744
He washes his hands and face.

00:52.887 --> 00:53.789
Scrub, scrub.

00:54.231 --> 00:55.649
He brushes his teeth.

00:56.305 --> 00:57.255
Brush, brush.

00:57.943 --> 00:59.516
He drinks a glass of water.

01:00.053 --> 01:00.824
Gulp, gulp.

01:01.711 --> 01:03.483
He puts on his pajamas.

01:03.817 --> 01:04.668
Wiggle, wiggle.

01:05.693 --> 01:07.425
Ben gets into bed.

